<div class="story"><p>Colony by the Sea is an oceanfront condominium complex in Duck consisting of 87 units, each with 1 or 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The one bedroom units have bunk beds built into the wall in the hallway to increase sleeping capacity. Most of the units have an ocean view although you might have to walk out onto the deck to see the ocean from the units further away from the beach. There is an oceanfront pool and two tennis courts. You can find Colony by the Sea just past <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/duck-ridge-shores.asp" title="Duck Ridge Shores">Duck Ridge Shores</a> as you travel north on Rte 12 and just before you get to the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/cc-byrum.asp" title="CC Byrum">CC Byrum</a>. </p>
